PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774199468
OL,3,CSunderland take the spoils as Tyne-
OL,4,CWear derby returns after 10 year
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FSunderland were given a hostile
OL,8,Freception on arrival into the city as
OL,9,Ffans lined the streets with flares and
OL,10,Fflags - with the windscreen of their
OL,11,Fteam bus cracked after objects were
OL,12,Fthrown at it as it approached the
OL,13,Fstadium.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/5
